{"entity":{"id":"recRt5yKqyKFuXNso","type":"chapter","slug":"recRt5yKqyKFuXNso","label":"Job.15","rawId":"recRt5yKqyKFuXNso","book":{"id":"recOA8nVVhKs30PSI","type":"book","slug":"job","label":"Job","subtitle":"Poetry-Wisdom","count":1070,"description":"42 chapters, 190 people, 6 places"}},"stats":{"verses":35,"people":2,"places":0,"events":1},"nodes":[{"id":"recRt5yKqyKFuXNso","type":"chapter","group":"focus","label":"Job.15","slug":"job_15","score":35},{"id":"recOA8nVVhKs30PSI","type":"book","group":"book","label":"Job","slug":"job","score":1070},{"id":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"God","slug":"god_1324","score":5},{"id":"recE1c6dLNGYPFRiW","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"Eliphaz","slug":"eliphaz_1145","score":1},{"id":"recMNT9RB1RJiLlYW","type":"event","group":"event","label":"Job's Trial","slug":"event-117","score":35}],"links":[{"source":"recRt5yKqyKFuXNso","target":"recOA8nVVhKs30PSI","label":"part of"},{"source":"recRt5yKqyKFuXNso","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recRt5yKqyKFuXNso","target":"recE1c6dLNGYPFRiW","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recRt5yKqyKFuXNso","target":"recMNT9RB1RJiLlYW","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recbABPVT6d964R0D","ref":"Job.15.1","text":"Then answered Eliphaz the Temanite, and said,","year":-1520},{"id":"recIXhokHv8NtOqbs","ref":"Job.15.2","text":"Should a wise man utter vain knowledge, and fill his belly with the east wind?","year":-1520},{"id":"recAb6saseRvdtGro","ref":"Job.15.3","text":"Should he reason with unprofitable talk? or with speeches wherewith he can do no good?","year":-1520},{"id":"reckXf46khxPF8X4A","ref":"Job.15.4","text":"Yea, thou castest off fear, and restrainest prayer before God.","year":-1520},{"id":"rechCkEP1zBDrbznm","ref":"Job.15.5","text":"For thy mouth uttereth thine iniquity, and thou choosest the tongue of the crafty.","year":-1520},{"id":"rechYaItDs89b6jPd","ref":"Job.15.6","text":"Thine own mouth condemneth thee, and not I: yea, thine own lips testify against thee.","year":-1520},{"id":"recSP3I0CyuOBg1en","ref":"Job.15.7","text":"Art thou the first man that was born? or wast thou made before the hills?","year":-1520},{"id":"recK0fI376WOgLF0H","ref":"Job.15.8","text":"Hast thou heard the secret of God? and dost thou restrain wisdom to thyself?","year":-1520}]}
